  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to show whether the Neo system is safe and works in
      people with heart failure. The study is currently in long-term follow up.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A prospective, randomized study describing the safety and efficacy of the Neo system in
      approximately 60 heart failure subjects with a left ventricular ejection fraction equal or
      less than 35 percent.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
